# React & UI

- Use functional components and named exports where the file already does
- Import UI from `@/components/ui/*` (shadcn-style Button, Badge, Separator)
- Section components live in `src/components/sections/`; layout in `src/components/layout/`
- Copy and static content: `src/data/content.ts`
- Prefer `container-editorial`, `section-padding`, and display type utilities from `src/index.css`
- Buttons support `href` for anchor CTAs; use shadcn variants (`default`, `outline`, `secondary`, `ghost`, `brand`)
